commit.title: Moving locating of yet non-located interpretation-time error to stm.ml.
commit.message:
Moving locating of yet non-located interpretation-time error to stm.ml.

The question is whether ensuring a location is the role of
Vernacentries.interp (excluding parts of process_transaction) or of
process_transaction (excluding query, perform, ... and other methods
calling interp).
